cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.HC. 

The paper focuses on designing intelligent robotic systems and proposes a deep model for learning actions from human demonstration video for robotic manipulation. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also involves video captioning and object detection, which are related to computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed deep model is based on deep neural networks, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper aims to improve the grasping performance of the robotic arm, which is related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
